result.name: The Junk Yard Dog Bar

reviews.text:
Amazing place to make friends and maintain friends. If you want to come back to a place years after … and still have friends to talk to this is your place ! 
I moved to HK after living in  the US and this is the quintessential Neighborhood bar. Great drinks relatively cheaper vs everything else available in the area. If you value good company and a good time over being in a pretentious place of which there are several in HK I would highly recommend this place!
Hidden gem with great service run by a real Napalese personality. First visit to HK... So glad I found this place. Will definitely come back
Great atmosphere, but it's 2019. This place needs to work on its single-use plastic policy if it wants to keep up
Home filling place. You can make good friends .  All away welcomeing.  The junkyard dog bar.

Small and neatly decorated bar. Drinks are not cheap, and similar to high end bars in Hong Kong, which this bar is not. The owner and hostess is rude and the only person working there which adds to waiting time for food and drinks
